<h2>{{subject}}</h2>

<div class="alert {{#if critical}}alert-danger{{else}}alert-warning{{/if}}">
  <strong>{{#if critical}}CRITICAL ALERT{{else}}SYSTEM ALERT{{/if}}</strong>
</div>

<p>The system has detected an issue that requires attention:</p>

<pre>{{message}}</pre>

<p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
<p><strong>Environment:</strong> {{environment}}</p>

<p>
  Please investigate this issue as {{#if critical}}soon as possible{{else}}time permits{{/if}}.
</p>

<a href="https://dashboard.performance-tracking.com/alerts" class="btn">View Alerts Dashboard</a> 